  "title": "Accounting Assistant会计助理",
  "description": "<h3></h3><h3>招聘职位 / Position</h3><p><strong>会计助理 / 财务出纳</strong><br /><strong>Accounting Assistant / Finance Clerk</strong></p><p>📍 <strong>工作地点 / Location：</strong> 新加坡<br />🕙 <strong>工作时间 / Working Hours：</strong> 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM<br />📅 <strong>工作制度 / Work Arrangement：</strong> 五天制（周一至周五 / Monday – Friday）</p><h2>岗位职责 / Job Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>负责日常出纳工作，包括收付款处理、现金及银行往来记录；<br />Handle daily cashiering duties including receipts, payments, and cash/bank transactions;</p></li><li><p>协助处理公司日常财务事务；<br />Assist with daily finance-related operations;</p></li><li><p>整理、归档及管理财务相关文件与凭证；<br />Organise, file and maintain financial documents and records;</p></li><li><p>协助会计完成其他财务及行政相关工作。<br />Support the accountant in other finance and administrative duties as required.</p></li></ul><h2>任职要求 / Job Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>具备基本会计或财务相关知识；<br />Basic knowledge in accounting or finance;</p></li><li><p>工作细心、有责任感，具备良好的执行力；<br />Detail-oriented, responsible and reliable;</p></li><li><p>能熟练使用基本办公软件（如 Excel、Word）；<br />Proficient in basic office software such as Excel and Word;</p></li><li><p>有新加坡相关财务或出纳经验者优先。<br />Prior accounting or finance experience in Singapore is an advantage.</p></li></ul><h2>薪资福利 / Salary & Benefits</h2><ul><li><p><strong>薪资 / Salary：</strong> SGD 2,500</p></li><li><p><strong>年假 / Annual Leave：</strong> 14 天</p></li><li><p>稳定工作时间，良好的工作与生活平衡<br />Stable working hours with good work-life balance</p></li></ul>",
